{"tid":1895650,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深圳透過中聯辦每天向香港捐贈10萬口罩　首批一百萬","createTime":"2020-02-24T16:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T16:41:54.000Z","uid":226984,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5c9654c7c90207797bf7a5964542a97b8ed7a0fa","tid":1895650,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:07:33.000Z","msg":"深圳市由今日起透過中聯辦，每天向香港捐贈10萬個口罩，首批100萬，支持香港做好防疫抗疫工作。<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦副主任楊健與深圳市長陳如桂出席捐贈儀式。<br />\n<br />\n楊健表示，中聯辦將在香港特區政府支持下，做好口罩接收和運送工作，並委托「全港社區抗疫連綫」做好口罩派發工作。<br />\n<br />\n陳如桂強調，深圳一直把支持香港做好疫情防控工作，擺在重要位置。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510557-20200224.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510557-20200224.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=2321e3b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510557-20200224.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c3cbf364\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510557-20200224.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"76f4fe1a27161110b77f83b39b0f0ce5c095d561","tid":1895650,"uid":226984,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:07:58.000Z","msg":"每日送病毒落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880b13f85b276ef58c7433744050d46e2ad0542e","tid":1895650,"uid":73381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:08:29.000Z","msg":"又黎0.01口罩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd51cf9f1b794fa14439678319da29dd0733e9b3","tid":1895650,"uid":108374,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:08:49.000Z","msg":"其他地區又準備鬧喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13617a1877ab1b671b6b307e2be83013805a515","tid":1895650,"uid":265840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,